id: pmc-mklv
title: Enable scheduled npm and GitHub auto release workflow
description: "Add a free GitHub Actions workflow for pm-changelog that runs daily and by manual dispatch, skips when no commits exist after the latest release tag, computes the next pm date-based release tag, updates npm and pm package version surfaces, regenerates changelog output with pm-changelog itself, runs release quality gates, commits release artifacts, publishes to npm, and creates a public GitHub release."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[4]: automation,github-actions,npm,release
created_at: "2026-05-23T21:53:29.093Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T21:59:31.243Z"
deadline: "2026-05-23T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "- .github/workflows/release.yml exists and is enabled for daily schedule plus workflow_dispatch.\\n- Workflow uses only free GitHub Actions features and repository GITHUB_TOKEN permissions.\\n- Workflow exits without publishing when HEAD has no diff from the latest release tag.\\n- Workflow updates package.json, package-lock.json, manifest.json, src/extension.ts, dist, and CHANGELOG.md before tagging.\\n- Workflow publishes npm with the NPM_TOKEN repository secret and creates a public GitHub release after all checks pass."
reviewer: steve
risk: high
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: v2026.05.23-6
resolution: "Implemented .github/workflows/release.yml with daily schedule, workflow_dispatch, no-change skip logic, date-based tag computation, version metadata updates, build/check/audit/pack gates, pm-changelog generated changelog output, release commit/tag push, npm publish with NPM_TOKEN, and GitHub release creation."
expected_result: "The repository has an enabled scheduled release workflow that publishes only when changes exist since the latest release tag and performs versioning, changelog generation, npm publish, and GitHub release creation after checks pass."
actual_result: "actionlint passed for ci.yml and release.yml; README documents NPM_TOKEN and automated release behavior; workflow uses free GitHub Actions schedule, workflow_dispatch, GITHUB_TOKEN contents write, and id-token write for npm provenance."
