close_reason: "Scheduled release workflow implemented and locally validated with actionlint, YAML parsing, README documentation, and release gate compatibility."
body: "This feature closes the missing automation gap: daily release automation must exist in-repo, be enabled, avoid duplicate publishes, and remain compatible with the package's self-hosted changelog workflow."
